  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-b905d465-4264-4dd6-84cb-03ff4475a91e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-adfdbfd1-00ab-48df-a58f-300a6b1ad782\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7149ea9e-bf1e-4569-8820-0dcdcde4d8c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>2023년 새해인사 이미지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8df987b2-4021-4292-8980-d93ee033e6da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-dfe0e66d-d4ea-4d0e-b220-20332a16625e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-11d204fc-0858-4c6c-aba4-78593c299c9a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">2023년 계묘년 설날이 다가옵니다. 벌써 이번 주말부터 시작되는 연휴가 다가오네요. 올해는 새해 복많이 받으시기 바랍니다. 진심으로요.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-72a2cf1b-78e3-4f5f-b358-9a43dd808603\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-17d65b45-cb23-49cb-b9d1-4eff87577f54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-11651630-7a68-4eba-82bf-472dc512d75d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e3e06c8f-9ae8-432b-9908-466d79be365f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">저는 개인적으로 다음 문구를 거의 매년 넣습니다. 매우 좋아하는 문구입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-6111d5aa-96d0-4fae-9132-4603b878f055\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b86439f9-7d3d-4168-bbee-40fe60c7bcd0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c037f90b-eae7-478b-8c27-870bdaa125f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fb4b64c5-6763-468a-a111-e09ef71d4aa1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-98dab352-117a-4e02-9f2d-9d5b91cd369d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">우리가 살아있다면,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-880560cb-ba85-404d-9729-7468f7830728\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-816e21d1-cdb1-47d7-ade1-b722940802e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">살아있는 동안에는 헛되이 살지 않는 것이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73133de1-5602-401a-9f9f-38190599d875\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6a571293-eb03-4d98-9596-6aa9d841a232\" style=\"color:#555555;\">매우 중요하다고 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-151eb1b5-155d-48b5-b4da-b678af135f85\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-218f6a86-9f29-4324-b36f-375df2043166\" style=\"color:#555555;\">약자에게 관심과 사랑을 베풀고, 간직한 물건을 아끼고,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-295d56e0-baa4-474c-a7e2-7a03c6062014\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e6082943-a4f5-45c5-9965-c5455536bf40\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다른 사람을 존경할 줄 알고 따뜻하게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c97fd585-d266-4bb0-af23-7135630d5340\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-04198e21-a551-47e3-9745-401f1750df5b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">감싸주는 마음이 우리를 행복하게 해준다고 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f58b975-2e5b-4ca5-8544-ec0142e2d359\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-550d0f34-a55e-4ba0-87d2-837d4253fed7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2023년 계묘년에는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9ecef9f-a332-49d5-85e7-04b10ffa4b0f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-70997a75-3f1d-478e-9cf6-06083e308c08\" style=\"color:#555555;\">우리 모두 행복한 사람이 되었으면 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f6497fca-2086-460c-aad8-262248ccf4bd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2dd12050-e29b-464c-8af8-6279275d3aac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">새해 복 많이 받으십시요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cdce997a-8836-4301-b739-7a6573f32d51\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cdb4d34b-b1a7-4430-bf92-5d729e00c6ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-s