\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222983527360/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ea1e340-f1b7-4b5e-bbeb-c6165594bfc7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da082cd4-b6b7-4dd4-90e9-26b455c72619\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6c40d7bd-376a-421b-a9a3-ab7067ff67a9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">바탕의 모양은 베지어툴로 그렸습니다. 이미지사이트에 많이 나오는 일반적인 설날 모양입니다. 색상은 C0 M10 Y20 K5입니다. 선 두께는 0.75mm입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c246d8b9-2e10-4b19-936e-4d04f7ec5e41\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1c5bc7fe-22c8-4435-b6b2-aca2e0fbbd32\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:841px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222983527360/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1875dc3f-38eb-46f7-9879-c82e15da87e6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ce33769-6fff-47b1-8ab9-7dcf3b8ea749\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-53d762f8-33d2-4f5b-96b0-181fced03d21\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">바탕의 산과 모양도 베지어나 그라데이션 툴로 하나하나 다 그렸습니다. 제가 제작한 이미지라 무료로 사용해서 쓰셔도 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-311ecb6b-5fb2-4140-a08f-f5b4888f9190\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fd478c92-809b-415d-b6bf-787f8a0ab518\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:828px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222983527360/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ecfe6324-ad0b-4bfe-920e-132cb920842c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26e30eeb-a50a-46e1-b084-cee27427d898\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b2aabe3b-e6ba-46c7-b00e-e41e145e869f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">서체도 무료서체를 사용했으니 다운로드해서 이미지로 활용하셔도 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a1718b8c-b1e0-4cef-b305-2fb17512c80e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5d18da7d-9981-4f9d-9e6f-b887545cea68\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6448179a-f7d0-40a7-97ab-ddf1ab504fad\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4cab1d43-cf36-45ca-bedf-7e4828e155a6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">최종 컨펌이미지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b356473-12d1-4cba-a481-d4531f2d07ec\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222983527360/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-49ffe8bc-848f-4037-8d1c-26815a33c60a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8f3ae2b-2f18-460a-a1ab-a75ef7591374\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-722fd630-ebb8-466f-817d-97ad15c37894\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b9fa87e4-7bb8-42dc-9855-4c5bdeef3897\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-33a2d549-0d7c-4938-9a43-58adc3243dbf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음은 영상을 만들어 올려드려 보겠습니다. 작은 이미지이고 디자인이지만 이 글을 보시는 분들이 잘 활용해 주셨으면 합니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bd5100cc-15c7-4abf-9dfc-b5fb00316ed7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222983527360#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
